OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining cloud will quickly clear,
OL,7,Fleaving a dry and largely clear
OL,8,Fevening and night. It will be warmer
OL,9,Fthan the previous night, with a humid
OL,10,Ffeel, especially in larger cities, and
OL,11,Flight winds throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FDry with hazy sunshine
OL,14,Finitially, the cloud gradually
OL,15,Fthickening from the west to give the
OL,16,Fodd shower, perhaps thunderstorm, late
OL,17,Fafternoon. Widely very warm, although
OL,18,Fcooler along coastal areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
